snippet.title: Top 80s and 90s "Other Sports" Card Sales on eBay
snippet.description:
These are the top "Other Sports" Card sales from the 80's and 90's that sold on eBay. This covers Golf Cards, Soccer Cards, Wrestling Cards, Tennis Cards and more.

Investing in Baseball Cards, Hockey Cards, Basketball Cards and Football Cards can be done on a budget and still yield a great investment. You don't need to spend thousands of dollars on a box chasing a hard to find Hit! 

The Junk Wax era is full of HOF'ers and Rookie Cards that will appreciate over the next 5-10 years. With some of these boxes still available for cheap, you can have multiple opportunities to pull a PSA 10 gradable gem!
